description: Svetlana Tikhanovskaya is in Lithuania after disputing Sunday's poll results she says were rigged.
title: Belarus election: Opposition leader Tikhanovskaya left 'for sake of her children'
title_page: Belarus election: Opposition leader Tikhanovskaya left 'for sake of her children' - BBC News
maintext: After the 2010 election, state TV ran "confessions" from detained opposition activists that looked similar to what we saw on Tuesday. Many people I have spoken to in Minsk back Ms Tikhanovskaya all the way, saying she had no choice but to flee in order to protect her children, as her husband is in prison.
